product.title: VEVOR Workbench Corner Brackets 48 lbs. Shop Table Bracket Kit 4mm Galvanized Steel for Heavy-Duty Deck Edge (8-Pieces)
product.description: 8 PCs Black T Brackets. Heavy Support, Tight Fixation and Match Your Decor. If you are looking for heavy-duty, industrial-level support for your wood piece? Look no further than you have found them. VEVOR's T mending plate is the ideal fastener to make your wood-to-wood connections firm and provide constant support for years to come. Bring your furniture back to its prime and keep the good times coming with VEVOR.
feature_bullets: Helps strengthen structural integrity of dock frames
Includes wood screws for secure mounting
descriptive_attributes: Powder-coated Carbon Steel: Features a 16-Gauge heavy carbon steel black powder-coated material. Our T bracket has superior corrosion resistance, weather resistance, and ultimate strength. It provides constant support for years to come. Our smooth and elegant black T mending plate is a perfect fit for your building decor

Fit for 6 in. or Larger Lumber: Length: 17-7/10 in., Height: 11-2/5 in., Width: 5 in.. Our T tie plate is designed for working with 6 in. or larger lumber. The black T bracket is used to support the joining of a cross beam and a support beam via the pre-drilled holes on the side. It is perfect for reinforcing joints and ensuring that furniture remains firm

Powerful and stable support: mounting hole dia.: 0.2 in.. Mounting hole distance: 3.4 in. compared with ordinary plates, with only 2 pre-drilled holes on each t-shaped bracket, ours has 3 pre-drilled holes on each for maximizing the holding strength of your furniture. Our T-shaped joint is an ideal fastener to make wood-to-wood connections remain in place with no excuses

Completed installation accessories provided: you can get 8 x T flat brackets and 16 x M6 screws in the package, thanks to the pre-drilled holes and compatible accessories, you can start making your furniture sturdy anytime, only 1-person is required to successfully finish the installation, saving you time and effort

Get more done: the T plate bracket provides an easy solution for indoor and outdoor DIY jobs around the house. It is perfect for strengthening roofs, pergolas, and rafting. It is also an excellent choice to apply to reinforce or repair tables, chests, screens, windows, beds, or any other home furniture where a T-shaped joint fastener is applicable, stop putting off those fix-it jobs, and take the first step now
